{"schema_version":1,"event_id":"sase-5l:000013:issue_created:sase-5l.12","timestamp":"2026-07-08T05:14:42Z","actor":"bryanbugyi34@gmail.com","operation":"issue_created","issue_id":"sase-5l.12","payload":{"kind":"issue_created","issue":{"id":"sase-5l.12","title":"doctor: add ulimits, inotify, truecolor deep checks","status":"open","issue_type":"phase","parent_id":"sase-5l","owner":"bryanbugyi34@gmail.com","assignee":"","created_at":"2026-07-08T05:14:42Z","created_by":"bryanbugyi34@gmail.com","updated_at":"2026-07-08T05:14:42Z","closed_at":null,"close_reason":null,"description":"Add deep checks. resources.ulimits: compare soft RLIMIT_NOFILE and RLIMIT_NPROC against a floor derived from configured runner concurrency. resources.inotify (Linux-only): read /proc/sys/fs/inotify/* and WARN when watch/instance limits are likely to force ACE inotify watchers into polling. terminal.truecolor (deep, low priority): WARN only when image-preview fidelity matters. Add tests. See research section 11 and the epic plan design file.","notes":"","design":"","model":"","is_ready_to_work":false,"changespec_name":"","changespec_bug_id":"","dependencies":[]}}}
